00:00:39.179 --> 00:00:44.929
Pop artist Andy Warhol states, "People should fall in love with their eyes closed." In this quote,

00:00:44.929 --> 00:00:50.839
he's referring to the magic people feel when they start to mean something to one another. It sounds ideal and spectacular,

00:00:51.449 --> 00:00:54.498
